Package: ros-rolling-image-geometry
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libopencv-dev, ros-rolling-sensor-msgs, ros-rolling-ros-workspace
Description: `image_geometry` contains C++ and Python libraries for interpreting images geometrically.
 It interfaces the calibration parameters in sensor_msgs/CameraInfo messages with OpenCV functions such as image rectification, much as cv_bridge interfaces ROS sensor_msgs/Image with OpenCV data types.
